Status of Interlibrary Loans Items May Be Incorrect!

Interlibrary Loan items that are "in transit" may show as "ready for pickup". Interlibrary loans that are ready for pick up may not show as "ready" when viewing holds. Please contact the library for more information on the status of your interlibrary loan items.
